{"tid":21683,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"到底男仔定女仔會比較容易俾人感動到","createTime":"2016-12-04T04:17:46.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-05T05:10:09.000Z","uid":17088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"377166b80f2d7b1735a296ac62c0b9c648c12834","tid":21683,"uid":17088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T04:17:46.000Z","msg":"假設你追緊一個人 佢本身對你無好感<br />\n但你持續咁對佢好好呀 關心佢一切呀<br />\n咁既情況下男仔會容易啲鍾意一個本身無好感既女仔定女仔容易啲鍾意一個本身無好感既男仔?<br />\n<br />\n定係其實不論男女 只要無feel就做咩都無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n各位點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d56730f3e669c9d139b832a1b4fef3082bedf47c","tid":21683,"uid":2510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T04:20:26.000Z","msg":"無feel乜都唔洗做架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家啲人冇咁易感動"},{"pid":"f5e0e5182fe21222452d2f78e7d9f9534dd1ab41","tid":21683,"uid":52190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T04:26:44.000Z","msg":"感動同鐘意係兩回事"},{"pid":"3d4c26e25f9560e1f8abefa299e44d2706c4e56d","tid":21683,"uid":52816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T04:32:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8946d582cc4d41fc1c274a895d52761351e6b768","tid":21683,"uid":52816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T04:35:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"713e876f1134418082b6ae322674b6245ebfb380","tid":21683,"uid":17088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T12:27:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講返自己先。如果有人死心不息，我個人只會覺得佢真係好嘔心。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你係巴打?<br />\n好少女仔會死纏 好似係"},{"pid":"82fc180bd144363d837d9927051a4631d1ae9f83","tid":21683,"uid":9668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T12:36:00.000Z","msg":"無好感 感動條鐵阿？<br />\n依家d人冷血架 <br />\n死左都冇人可憐 眼尾都唔望<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid